# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Sefay V1.02 — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── App ───────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3001

# ── Supabase ──────────────────────────
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-min-32-chars

# ── Direct Postgres (Supavisor, TRANSACTION mode) ─────
# Required by PgPoolModule/TenantSessionService for RLS-enforced hot paths
# (SET LOCAL app.tenant_id). Get from Supabase dashboard → Settings → Database
# → Connection Pooling → "Transaction" mode connection string (port 6543).
# Do NOT use the session-mode or direct-connection string here.
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.your-project:password@aws-region.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres
PG_POOL_MAX=10
# Keep false until DATABASE_URL is live AND migration 075 is applied — see
# TASKS.md "SAFETY & SCALE INITIATIVE" before ever setting this to true.
POOLED_INVOICE_WRITES_ENABLED=false
# Same rule, gated on migration 076 instead of 075.
POOLED_STOCK_WRITES_ENABLED=false
# Same rule again — AND requires a dedicated non-BYPASSRLS Postgres role
# backing DATABASE_URL, not the default Supabase "postgres" role (see
# loyalty.service.ts for why). Do not enable based on migration 075 alone.
POOLED_LOYALTY_WRITES_ENABLED=false

# ── Auth ──────────────────────────────
# Must be at least 32 characters random string
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret-minimum-32-characters-here
JWT_EXPIRY=15m
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRY=7d

# ── Redis ─────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ── Payments ──────────────────────────
# Values: stripe | mock
PAYMENT_PROVIDER=mock
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ── Email ─────────────────────────────
# Leave empty to use mock mode
RESEND_API_KEY=
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@sefay.com

# ── Frontend ──────────────────────────
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000